RACE.RACE_TEXT: GULFSTREAM PARK RACE 1 1M 70Y All Weather Track CR: 70. Maiden Claiming Purse 19000. FOR MAIDENS, FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 118 lbs.; Older, 125 lbs. Claiming Price $12,500 If no three-year-olds are entered, older weight will revert to 122lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: LOVE UNLIMITED had a rank start, stalked along the inside, angled out and was coaxed from the three path midway around the far turn, took aim from the five path at the top of the lane, rallied past a pair of inner foes, and was up in the final sixteenth. RANSOM STYLE settled in range from the four path, stuck a head in front early around the far turn, was under right handed urging from the three path into the stretch, but was caught passing the sixteenth pole to place. KIT CAN RUN prompted the pace while under a hold in the three path, bid under a drive around the far turn, kept on while shifting to the rail down the lane, but evened out late to show. REACHING STRIDE bumped with an inner foe at the start, rated in the four path, was roused while tipping out to the five path into the far turn, fanned out to the nine path into the stretch, and mildly improved. CARAVANA was held up in the two path, cued midway around the far turn, angled out to the seven path into the stretch, and finished evenly. WITCHING HOUR travelled in the six path around the first turn and raced in midpack from the five path down the backstretch, was driven from the six path into the stretch, but faded. ANTRIM tracked in the three path but dropped back around the far turn. I LOVE IRELAND set the pace in the two path, was ridden from the rail around the far turn, but gaveway. HEART OF THE BEAST broke slow, trailed in the four path down the backside, and never menaced. GLACIE INHERITANCE bumped with an outer foe at the start, was wellback along the inside early and could never get involved.
